--- !u!114 &1452768354
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1452768348}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c2163f048da8d624286c5daba35a3076, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - speakerName: Narasi
    profile: {fileID: -7771728774132427043, guid: 6809b27ca40283248be0310e4d5f4ef1, type: 3}
    text: '*Tiba-tiba ada orang asing mendekat ke arah Rara...*'
    choices: []
  - speakerName: Paman Baik
    profile: {fileID: 414440879778542897, guid: d7769e879c67f7d44942d01f783848db, type: 3}
    text: '"Hei dek, bentar ya~!"'
    choices: []
  - speakerName: Rara (hati)
    profile: {fileID: -307426207498796367, guid: b337f726c99b2184ba032db933c4af66, type: 3}
    text: Eh? Siapa ini? Rara nggak pernah lihat orang ini sebelumnya...
    choices: []
  - speakerName: Paman Baik
    profile: {fileID: -1209331726834910066, guid: 9faab9d09b6eba44fb09370ec6e1e75c, type: 3}
    text: '"Mau permen nggak? Enak banget lho~

      Om punya banyak di warung,
      ikut bentar aja ya, deket kok! tuh warungya Om"'
    choices: []
  - speakerName: Rara (hati)
    profile: {fileID: -621021955452869361, guid: 74e32d7b50454b44fa273c2384918263, type: 3}
    text: 'Tunggu... Rara nggak kenal orang ini sama sekali!

      Dia nawarin permen
      DAN mau ngajak Rara pergi... INI NGGAK BENER!'
    choices: []
  - speakerName: Paman Baik
    profile: {fileID: -1209331726834910066, guid: 9faab9d09b6eba44fb09370ec6e1e75c, type: 3}
    text: '"Ayo dong, nggak usah malu-malu~ Sebentar aja kok!"'
    choices: []
  - speakerName: Rara
    profile: {fileID: -621021955452869361, guid: 74e32d7b50454b44fa273c2384918263, type: 3}
    text: Gimana Rara harus merespons orang ini?
    choices: []
  - speakerName: Narasi
    profile: {fileID: -7771728774132427043, guid: 6809b27ca40283248be0310e4d5f4ef1, type: 3}
    text: 'INGAT: Orang asing yang kasih hadiah atau ngajak pergi = TANDA BAHAYA!

      Selalu
      tolak dengan tegas dan pergi ke tempat yang rame!'
    choices: []
